Alien: Isolation - Corporate Lockdown DLC (c) SEGA

Release Date : 11/2014 Protection : Steam

Welcome to Corporate Lockdown, the first expansion pack for Alien:
Isolation. This pack features three all-new maps:for Survivor Mode, a
time-based challenge to test your skills. Can you evade the Alien for
long enough to survive or will you try to take the Alien head-on? -
Three new maps, stretching from the Corporate Penthouse to the
Medlabs. - New playable character Ransome gives you the firepower to
take the fight to your enemies.
